<h2>Amending a Certificate of Registration</h2>

<h3>Medical Certificate of Registration Amendments</h3>
<p>When submitting a request to amend your MEDICAL registration, you may either write a letter describing the necessary change or complete <a title="RC Form 226-2" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#2262">RC Form 226-2</a>, indicating the change in item 3. Both methods require reference of the registration number and inclusion any additional information needed to process your request.</p>
<blockquote style="font-style:normal;">
	<p><strong>Name and/or Ownership Change</strong><br/>See Regulatory Guide 8.2: <a title="Regulatory Guide 8.2, Guidelines for Issuing Certificates of Registration Due to a Change in Name and/or Ownership" href="/radiation/regulatory-guides.aspx#82">Guidelines for Issuing Certificates of Registration Due to a Change in Name and/or Ownership</a></p>
	<p><strong>Radiation Safety Officer Change</strong><br/>Complete appropriate section of <a title="RC Form 42-3, RSO Information for Registration" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#423">RC Form 42-3, RSO Information for Registration</a></p>
	<p><strong>Deleting an X-Ray Machine</strong><br/>Complete and submit <a title="RC Form 18-R, Radiation Machine Transfer/Disposal Form" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#18R">RC Form 18-R, Radiation Machine Transfer/Disposal Form</a></p>
</blockquote>

<h3>Industrial Certificate of Registration Amendments</h3>
<p>When submitting a request to amend your INDUSTRIAL registration, you may write a letter describing the necessary change or complete <a title="RC Form 226-3" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#2263">RC Form 226-3</a>, indicating the change in item 9. Either way, always reference your registration number and include any additional information needed to process your request.</p>
<blockquote style="font-style:normal;">
	<p><strong>Name and/or Ownership Change</strong><br/>See Regulatory Guide 8.2: <a title="Regulatory Guide 8.2, Guidelines for Issuing Certificates of Registration Due to a Change in Name and/or Ownership" href="/radiation/regulatory-guides.aspx#82">Guidelines for Issuing Certificates of Registration Due to a Change in Name and/or Ownership</a></p>
	<p><strong>Radiation Safety Officer Change</strong><br/>Submit a letter requesting the change with documentation of training and experience with the type of x-ray equipment you are registered for.</p>
	<p><strong>Deleting an X-Ray Machine</strong><br/>Complete and submit <a title="RC Form 18-R, Radiation Machine Transfer/Disposal Form" href="/radiation/forms.aspx#18R">RC Form 18-R, Radiation Machine Transfer/Disposal Form</a></p>
</blockquote>

